      <p>PACT is a 36 month collaborative project, which aims 1) to assess existing knowledge about the relation between security and privacy and the role played by trust and concern; 2) to collect empirical evidence through a panEuropean survey on the public perception of the relation between privacy, fundamental rights, and security; 3) to analyze the main factors that  affect public assessment of the security and privacy implications of given security technology.
      </div>
  

  
    
      FP7-SECURITY-Call4
  
</li>
