      </div>
  

      <span class="subject">
  
    
      <a href="/project/ditsef"><code>DITSEF</code> - </a>
      </span>
  

      <span class="subject">
  
    
      <a href="/project/ditsef">Digital &amp; Innovative Technologies for Security &amp; Efficiency of First responder operations</a>
      </span>
  

      <div class="description">
  
    
      <p>DITSEF aims at increasing the effectiveness and safety of First Responders by optimal information gathering and sharing with their higher command levels.<br />
DITSEF will provide<br />
- Self-organising, robust ad-hoc communications where the existing infrastructure may be compromised, allowing communication between First Responders and between them and their command level<br />
- Accurate novel 3D positioning in indoor environments<br />
- Sensors that offer a reliable overview of the situation and of the potential threats (explosives, chemicals, fire, etc.).<br />
      </div>
  

  
    
