      <div class="description">
  
    
      <p>The project will cover several needs of a school library like digitizing, archiving, indexing and searching in ac-cordance with an asynchronous educational platform with remote access properties. The project?s target is an automated archiving-indexing tool that permits daily addition of an extensive amount of information and the en-couragement of e-Learning in secondary school students through the provision of selected, quality information.
      </div>
  

  
    
      GSRT/Ministry of Development
  
