      <p>The project aims to create an integrated system for controlling the access of persons in athletic organizations. The system consists of two subsystems: the first is dedicated to control the access of the certified persons, while the second is dedicated to control the access of the spectators.</p>
      </div>
  

  
    
      GSRT/Ministry of Development
  
